import React from 'react'
import { Wrapper,Container,TitleContainer,Title,FollowersCounter } from './styles'

function Header() {
    return (
        <Wrapper>
            <Container>
                <TitleContainer>
                    <Title>Social Media Dashboard</Title>
                    <FollowersCounter>Total Followers : 23,004</FollowersCounter>
                </TitleContainer>
            </Container>
        </Wrapper>
    )
}

export default Header
